<t align='center' color='#339933'>SERVER INFO FAQ</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>To build a base you must purchase a territory flag. You can purchase a territory from the office at traders. When you purchase a territory you get a flag pole that you can place anywhere you choose considering the rules. DO NOT place flagpole base inside of objects where it cant be stolen, it will be deleted.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>To use Virtual Garage "VG" a territory is needed. To access the garage use the XM8 VG App. Admins are not responsible for and will not replace vehicles not stored in the garage.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Vehicles parked on floors or near other objects will explode, sometimes even on unlevel ground. This is an Exile bug that has been around forever. Please do not ask for replacements.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Bases are deleted from the database every 5 days if you do not pay your protection. If your base is gone then your protection fees were not paid on time. Admins will not replace bases if they protection was not paid on time.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Vehicles delete everyday if not used, vehicles stored in VG are protected from this rule.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>VG storage is based on territory level.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>If you need help with something then join our discord and ask an Admin for help Discord.gg/RGN</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Video or picture evidence is needed to ban disruptive players, post video/screenshots in our forums</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Bounties can be placed on other players for a fee at the Office Trader under MOST WANTED.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>You can Hack, Grind, and Lockpick doors and vehicles, Watch out for safes rigged with explosives. Mine detectors are your best friend when raiding bases. Make sure to scan with a mine detector before breaking into things.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Some vehicles can be claimed with codelocks.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Defibs are not required on this server, you have a total of 3 revives before having to respawn.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Knives are needed to pick locks, and to break into almost anything.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Most everything on the server is destructable, bullets go through mud huts and destroy building and walls. Some bridges can be demolished with satchels at their base.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Vector building is enabled, use your arrow keys to manipulate objects.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>We use respect based loadouts for respawn and the ranking system.</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>If shit talking, foul language, and things of this nature offend your delicate feelings then you should probably move along. We do not cater to whiners, trolls, or immature players. This is a mature community. Toxic players will be banned...</t><br /><br />
<t align='center' color='#E48A36'>Have fun, stay reckless, but remember its just a game.</t><br /><br />